==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Masterful
<hw>Mas"ter*ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Inclined to play the master; domineering; imperious;
arbitrary.</def> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having the skill or power of a master; indicating or
expressing power or mastery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His <qex>masterful</qex>, pale face.</q> <rj><qau>Mrs.
Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Masterfully</ent>⟦br⟧
